p>Panoramagic hoods are the perfect companion of your range cookers, that decorate the home thanks to their rounded shapes forged in pure steel with painstakingly made details.\\u00a0</p><p></p><p>They are true gems of professionalism, designed for the kitchen in your home. They are available in a range of selected colors or in RAL Classic shades on request, combined with fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Front LED bar</li><li>Painted steel body, AISI 304 stainless steel (only inox version)</li><li>Anodized aluminum filters</li><li>Automatic filter cleaning warning light</li><li>Maximum air flow 600\\u00a0CFM</li><li>Maximum power 450 W</li><li>Four-speed backlit touch controls</li><li>Flue outlet hole 5\\u2033 7/8\\u00a0</li><li>3 speeds + intensive</li><li>Automatic delayed shutdown </li></ul><p></p><p><strong>California Proposition 65</strong></p><p>WARNING: Cancer and Reproductive Harm</p><p><a href=\\\"http://www.P65Warnings.ca.gov\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">www.P65Warnings.ca.gov</a></p></div> <div><div><div><video preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/R4yyFfox7zU.mp4\\\">               Your browser does not support the video tag.            </video></div><div><video preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/it-h3Gfhsuo.mp4\\\">               Your browser does not support the video tag.            </video></div></div></div><br/><br/><strong>Freight Charges May Apply</strong><br/><br/></div> </div> <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_features\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" data-slug=\\\"features\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_features\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Features</span> </span></h3> <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_features\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_features\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"> <div><div><div>Unique Design Of Panoramagic</div><div>A tradition of the contemporary kitchen that withstands the test of time by combining cutting-edge technology with Italian cultural design to the kitchen. Panoramagic revolutionize the panorama of the domestic kitchen in an updated form and with a full range of solutions to fit into any interior design.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Unique Design Of Panoramagic\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1472.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div>A Tradition Of The Contemporary Kitchen That Withstands The Test Of Time.</div><div>Aesthetics is important, but it\\u2019s not all. It is essential to have the best technologies available to cook well and with pleasure. ILVE puts all its experience and research at your service, offering solutions that combine top-level performance and maximum simplicity, safety and user-friendliness: to always guarantee the best satisfaction.</div><div><img alt=\\\"A Tradition Of The Contemporary Kitchen That Withstands The Test Of Time.\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1473.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div>Four-Speed Controls (3 + Intensive)</div><div>3 speed including intensive mode provides 600 cfm (850 cfm on select models) to remove smoke and heat to keep your kitchen feeling fresh</div><div><img alt=\\\"Four-Speed Controls (3 + Intensive)\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/2400.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div>Automatic Delayed Shutdown</div><div>Leave the kitchen after you are done cooking and let the hood continue\\u00a0removing unwanted smoke, turning off by itself with the automatic delayed shutdown mode.\\u00a0</div><div><img alt=\\\"Automatic delayed shutdown\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/2402.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div>Anodized Aluminum Filters</div><div>Range hood filter made with high-quality anodized aluminum, is designed to capture and hold airborne grease released from cooking.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Anodized aluminum filters\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/2403.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div>Front LED  Bar</div><div>Illuminates your cooking area for enhanced visibility</div><div><img alt=\\\"Front LED bar\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/2404.jpg\\\"/></div></div> </div> </div> </div> <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_specification\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" data-slug=\\\"specification\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_specification\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Specifications</span> </span></h3> <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_specification\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_specification\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"> <table><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Brand</th><td>ILVE</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Series</th><td>Panoramagic</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Appliance Category</th><td>Hood</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\"><br><b>Appearance</b></br></th><td></td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Color</th><td>Stainless Steel</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Color Family</th><td>Stainless Steel</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Design Style</th><td>Modern</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Trim</th><td>Stainless Steel</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Noblesse Frames</th><td>No</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\"><br><b>Dimensions</b></br></th><td></td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Exterior Width</th><td>36\\u2033</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Width</th><td>35 7/8\\u2033</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Depth</th><td>22\\u2033</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Height</th><td>48 7/8\\u2033</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Product Weight (lbs)</th><td>77</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\"><br><b>Style</b></br></th><td></td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Style</th><td>Chimney Style</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Type</th><td>Wall Mount</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\"><br><b>Technical Details</b></br